sirikali (1.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=low
  [Mhogo Mchungu]
  * New Features
     -- Maintanance release.
     -- FIX BUG: Dont generate an update warning prompt on startup when
        auto check for updates is set but the application is started while
        the system has no internet connection.
     -- FIX BUG: Dont auto delete mount folders when a volumes was
        unmounted outside of SiriKali.
     -- FIX BUG: Populate $PATH variable properly before calling backends
        since some backends fails without it.
     -- FIX BUG: The build process failed to build on Qt4

